- Home Page:
      theme:
             dictionary:
                    colors:
                          brand: &brand_blue "#0ea5e9"
                          brand_dark: &brand_dark "#0369a1"
                          brand_light: &brand_light "#e0f2fe"
                          danger: &danger_red "#ef4444"
                          bg_page: &bg_page "#f8fafc"
                    font_sizes:
                          title: &title_size "50px"
             
             library:
                     elements:
                          button: 
                               background: *brand_blue
                               color: white
                               padding: "12px 24px"
                               border-radius: "8px"
                               border: "none"
                               font-weight: "bold"

      style:
          background-color: *bg_page
          padding: "40px"
          # Smart Reach-Inside Styling
          h1:
             color: *brand_dark
          h2:
             color: *brand_blue

      content:
             - h1: "üìù Welcome to Outline!"
             - p: |
                 Outline is a **simple language** that turns your ideas into a website *instantly*. 
                 You write in a list format, and Outline handles the heavy lifting.

             - section:
                  style:
                      background: "white"
                      padding: "20px"
                      border-radius: "15px"
                      margin: "20px 0"
                      border: "1px solid #e2e8f0"
                  content:
                      - h2: "1. The Basics & Markdown"
                      - p: "This paragraph contains **Bold**, *Italics*, and a [Link](https://google.com)."
                      - p: |
                          ### Markdown List Test:
                          - Simple to learn
                          - Powerful to use
                          - `Code blocks supported`

             - box:
                  style:
                      background: *brand_light
                      padding: "30px"
                      border-left: f"5px solid {*brand_blue}"
                      display: "block"
                      border-radius: "0 12px 12px 0"
                  content:
                      - h2: "2. Nesting & Custom Style"
                      - h1:
                          content: "I am a Large Custom Title"
                          style:
                              font size: *title_size
                              color: *brand_dark
                      - p: "I am inside a nested sky-blue box container with high contrast text."

             - section:
                  style:
                      display: "flex"
                      gap: "20px"
                      margin-top: "20px"
                  content:
                      - button: "**Click Me** (Library Style)"
                      - button:
                          content: "Secondary Action"
                          style:
                              background: "white"
                              color: *brand_blue
                              border: f"2px solid {*brand_blue}"

             - footer:
                  style:
                      margin-top: "50px"
                      border-top: "1px solid #e2e8f0"
                      padding-top: "20px"
                      color: "#64748b"
                  content: "Happy Building! üöÄ"